#. <section class="sutta" id="sn54.13"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn54.13:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 54"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 54"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn54.13:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga"
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn54.13:0.3"
msgid "13. Paṭhamaānandasutta"
msgstr "13. With Ānanda (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.329"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.13:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn54.13:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ "
"abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā ānando "
"bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Ānanda went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, "
"and said to him:"

#. VAR: ekadhammo → eko dhammo (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "sn54.13:1.3"
msgid ""
"“atthi nu kho, bhante, ekadhammo bhāvito bahulīkato cattāro dhamme "
"paripūreti, cattāro dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā satta dhamme paripūrenti, "
"satta dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā dve dhamme paripūrentī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Sir, is there one thing that, when developed and cultivated, fulfills four "
"things; and those four things, when developed and cultivated, fulfill seven "
"things; and those seven things, when developed and cultivated, fulfill two "
"things?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.13:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Atthi kho, ānanda, ekadhammo bhāvito bahulīkato cattāro dhamme paripūreti, "
"cattāro dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā satta dhamme paripūrenti, satta dhammā "
"bhāvitā bahulīkatā dve dhamme paripūrentī”ti."
msgstr "“There is, Ānanda.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
#. VAR: ekadhammo → eko dhammo (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "sn54.13:3.1"
msgid ""
"“Katamo pana, bhante, ekadhammo bhāvito bahulīkato cattāro dhamme "
"paripūreti, cattāro dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā satta dhamme paripūrenti, "
"satta dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā dve dhamme paripūrentī”ti?"
msgstr "“Sir, what is that one thing?”"

msgctxt "sn54.13:3.2"
msgid ""
"“Ānāpānassatisamādhi kho, ānanda, ekadhammo bhāvito bahulīkato cattāro "
"satipaṭṭhāne paripūreti, cattāro satipaṭṭhānā bhāvitā bahulīkatā satta "
"bojjhaṅge paripūrenti, satta bojjhaṅgā bhāvitā bahulīkatā vijjāvimuttiṃ "
"paripūrenti."
msgstr ""
"“Immersion due to mindfulness of breathing is one thing that, when developed "
"and cultivated, fulfills the four kinds of mindfulness meditation. And the "
"four kinds of mindfulness meditation, when developed and cultivated, fulfill "
"the seven awakening factors. And the seven awakening factors, when developed "
"and cultivated, fulfill knowledge and freedom."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.13:4.1"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃ bhāvito, ānanda, ānāpānassatisamādhi kathaṃ bahulīkato cattāro "
"satipaṭṭhāne paripūreti?"
msgstr ""
"And how is mindfulness of breathing developed and cultivated so as to "
"fulfill the four kinds of mindfulness meditation?"

msgctxt "sn54.13:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idhānanda, bhikkhu araññagato vā rukkhamūlagato vā suññāgāragato vā nisīdati "
"pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā ujuṃ kāyaṃ paṇidhāya parimukhaṃ satiṃ upaṭṭhapetvā."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant has gone to a wilderness, or to the root of a tree, or "
"to an empty hut, sits down cross-legged, with their body straight, and "
"establishes mindfulness right there."

msgctxt "sn54.13:4.3"
msgid "So satova assasati, satova passasati."
msgstr "Just mindful, they breathe in. Mindful, they breathe out."

msgctxt "sn54.13:4.4"
msgid ""
"Dīghaṃ vā assasanto ‘dīghaṃ assasāmī’ti pajānāti, dīghaṃ vā passasanto ‘"
"dīghaṃ passasāmī’ti pajānāti … pe …"
msgstr ""
"When breathing in heavily they know: ‘I’m breathing in heavily.’ When "
"breathing out heavily they know: ‘I’m breathing out heavily.’ …"

msgctxt "sn54.13:4.5"
msgid ""
"‘paṭinissaggānupassī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘paṭinissaggānupassī "
"passasissāmī’ti sikkhati."
msgstr ""
"They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in observing letting go.’ They "
"practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out observing letting go.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.330"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.13:5.1"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, ānanda, bhikkhu dīghaṃ vā assasanto ‘dīghaṃ assasāmī’ti "
"pajānāti, dīghaṃ vā passasanto ‘dīghaṃ passasāmī’ti pajānāti;"
msgstr ""
"When a mendicant is breathing in heavily they know: ‘I’m breathing in "
"heavily.’ When breathing out heavily they know: ‘I’m breathing out heavily.’"

msgctxt "sn54.13:5.2"
msgid "rassaṃ vā … pe …"
msgstr "…"

msgctxt "sn54.13:5.3"
msgid ""
"‘passambhayaṃ kāyasaṅkhāraṃ assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘passambhayaṃ "
"kāyasaṅkhāraṃ passasissāmī’ti sikkhati—"
msgstr ""
"They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in stilling the physical process.’ "
"They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out stilling the physical process.’"

msgctxt "sn54.13:5.4"
msgid ""
"kāye kāyānupassī, ānanda, bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye viharati ātāpī sampajāno "
"satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"At such a time a mendicant is meditating by observing an aspect of the body—"
"keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world."

msgctxt "sn54.13:5.5"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "sn54.13:5.6"
msgid "Kāyaññatarāhaṃ, ānanda, etaṃ vadāmi, yadidaṃ—assāsapassāsaṃ."
msgstr "Because the breath is a certain aspect of the body, I say."

msgctxt "sn54.13:5.7"
msgid ""
"Tasmātihānanda, kāye kāyānupassī bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye viharati ātāpī "
"sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Therefore, at such a time a mendicant is meditating by observing an aspect "
"of the body—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the "
"world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.13:6.1"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, ānanda, bhikkhu ‘pītippaṭisaṃvedī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, "
msgstr ""
"There’s a time when a mendicant practices like this: ‘I’ll breathe in "
"experiencing rapture … "

msgctxt "sn54.13:6.2"
msgid "sukhappaṭisaṃvedī … pe …"
msgstr "bliss …"

msgctxt "sn54.13:6.3"
msgid "cittasaṅkhārappaṭisaṃvedī …"
msgstr "mind …’ …"

msgctxt "sn54.13:6.4"
msgid ""
"‘passambhayaṃ cittasaṅkhāraṃ assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘passambhayaṃ "
"cittasaṅkhāraṃ passasissāmī’ti sikkhati—"
msgstr ""
"They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in stilling the mental processes.’ "
"They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out stilling the mental processes.’"

msgctxt "sn54.13:6.5"
msgid ""
"vedanāsu vedanānupassī, ānanda, bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye viharati ātāpī "
"sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"At such a time a mendicant is meditating by observing an aspect of feelings—"
"keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world."

msgctxt "sn54.13:6.6"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "sn54.13:6.7"
msgid ""
"Vedanāññatarāhaṃ, ānanda, etaṃ vadāmi, yadidaṃ—assāsapassāsānaṃ sādhukaṃ "
"manasikāraṃ."
msgstr ""
"Because close focus on the breath is a certain aspect of feelings, I say."

msgctxt "sn54.13:6.8"
msgid ""
"Tasmātihānanda, vedanāsu vedanānupassī bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye viharati ātāpī "
"sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. (2)"
msgstr ""
"Therefore, at such a time a mendicant is meditating by observing an aspect "
"of feelings—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the "
"world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.13:7.1"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, ānanda, bhikkhu ‘cittappaṭisaṃvedī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘"
"cittappaṭisaṃvedī passasissāmī’ti sikkhati;"
msgstr ""
"There’s a time when a mendicant practices like this: ‘I’ll breathe in "
"experiencing the mind.’ They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out "
"experiencing the mind.’"

msgctxt "sn54.13:7.2"
msgid "abhippamodayaṃ cittaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in gladdening the mind …"

msgctxt "sn54.13:7.3"
msgid "samādahaṃ cittaṃ …"
msgstr "immersing the mind in samādhi …"

msgctxt "sn54.13:7.4"
msgid ""
"‘vimocayaṃ cittaṃ assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘vimocayaṃ cittaṃ passasissāmī’ti "
"sikkhati—"
msgstr ""
"freeing the mind.’ They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out freeing the "
"mind.’"

msgctxt "sn54.13:7.5"
msgid ""
"citte cittānupassī, ānanda, bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye viharati ātāpī sampajāno "
"satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"At such a time a mendicant is meditating by observing an aspect of the mind—"
"keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world."

msgctxt "sn54.13:7.6"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "sn54.13:7.7"
msgid ""
"Nāhaṃ, ānanda, muṭṭhassatissa asampajānassa ānāpānassatisamādhibhāvanaṃ "
"vadāmi."
msgstr ""
"Because there is no development of immersion due to mindfulness of breathing "
"for someone who is unmindful and lacks awareness, I say."

msgctxt "sn54.13:7.8"
msgid ""
"Tasmātihānanda, citte cittānupassī bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye viharati ātāpī "
"sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. (3)"
msgstr ""
"Therefore, at such a time a mendicant is meditating by observing an aspect "
"of the mind—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the "
"world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.331"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.13:8.1"
msgid "Yasmiṃ samaye, ānanda, bhikkhu aniccānupassī … pe …"
msgstr ""
"There’s a time when a mendicant practices like this: ‘I’ll breathe in "
"observing impermanence …"

msgctxt "sn54.13:8.2"
msgid "virāgānupassī …"
msgstr "fading away …"

msgctxt "sn54.13:8.3"
msgid "nirodhānupassī …"
msgstr "cessation …"

msgctxt "sn54.13:8.4"
msgid ""
"‘paṭinissaggānupassī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘paṭinissaggānupassī "
"passasissāmī’ti sikkhati—"
msgstr ""
"letting go.’ They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out observing letting "
"go.’"

msgctxt "sn54.13:8.5"
msgid ""
"dhammesu dhammānupassī, ānanda, bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye viharati ātāpī "
"sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"At such a time a mendicant is meditating by observing an aspect of "
"principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the "
"world."

msgctxt "sn54.13:8.6"
msgid ""
"So yaṃ taṃ hoti abhijjhādomanassānaṃ pahānaṃ taṃ paññāya disvā sādhukaṃ "
"ajjhupekkhitā hoti."
msgstr ""
"Having seen with wisdom the giving up of desire and aversion, they watch "
"closely over with equanimity."

msgctxt "sn54.13:8.7"
msgid ""
"Tasmātihānanda, dhammesu dhammānupassī bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye viharati ātāpī "
"sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. (4)"
msgstr ""
"Therefore, at such a time a mendicant is meditating by observing an aspect "
"of principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the "
"world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.13:9.1"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ bhāvito kho, ānanda, ānāpānassatisamādhi evaṃ bahulīkato cattāro "
"satipaṭṭhāne paripūreti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how immersion due to mindfulness of breathing is developed and "
"cultivated so as to fulfill the four kinds of mindfulness meditation."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.13:10.1"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃ bhāvitā cānanda, cattāro satipaṭṭhānā kathaṃ bahulīkatā satta "
"bojjhaṅge paripūrenti?"
msgstr ""
"And how are the four kinds of mindfulness meditation developed and "
"cultivated so as to fulfill the seven awakening factors?"

msgctxt "sn54.13:10.2"
msgid "Yasmiṃ samaye, ānanda, bhikkhu kāye kāyānupassī viharati—"
msgstr "Whenever a mendicant meditates by observing an aspect of the body,"

#. VAR: upaṭṭhitāssa → upaṭṭhitā tassa (bj) | upaṭṭhitassa (s1-3) | upaṭṭhitasati (pts1) | upaṭṭhitassati (mr)
msgctxt "sn54.13:10.3"
msgid "upaṭṭhitāssa tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno sati hoti asammuṭṭhā."
msgstr "their mindfulness is established and lucid."

msgctxt "sn54.13:10.4"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, ānanda, bhikkhuno upaṭṭhitā sati hoti asammuṭṭhā—"
"satisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, satisambojjhaṅgaṃ "
"tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, satisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno "
"bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati."
msgstr ""
"At such a time, a mendicant has activated the awakening factor of "
"mindfulness; they develop it and perfect it."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.13:11.1"
msgid ""
"So tathā sato viharanto taṃ dhammaṃ paññāya pavicinati pavicarati "
"parivīmaṃsamāpajjati."
msgstr ""
"As they live mindfully in this way they investigate, explore, and inquire "
"into that principle with wisdom."

msgctxt "sn54.13:11.2"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, ānanda, bhikkhu tathā sato viharanto taṃ dhammaṃ paññāya "
"pavicinati pavicarati parivīmaṃsamāpajjati—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.13:11.3"
msgid ""
"dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, "
"dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgaṃ tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, "
"dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. "
"(2)"
msgstr ""
"At such a time, a mendicant has activated the awakening factor of "
"investigation of principles; they develop it and perfect it."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.332"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.13:12.1"
msgid ""
"Tassa taṃ dhammaṃ paññāya pavicinato pavicarato parivīmaṃsamāpajjato "
"āraddhaṃ hoti vīriyaṃ asallīnaṃ."
msgstr ""
"As they investigate principles with wisdom in this way their energy is "
"roused up and unflagging."

msgctxt "sn54.13:12.2"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, ānanda, bhikkhuno taṃ dhammaṃ paññāya pavicinato pavicarato "
"parivīmaṃsamāpajjato āraddhaṃ hoti vīriyaṃ asallīnaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"At such a time, a mendicant has activated the awakening factor of energy; "
"they develop it and perfect it."

msgctxt "sn54.13:12.3"
msgid ""
"vīriyasambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, vīriyasambojjhaṅgaṃ "
"tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, vīriyasambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno "
"bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. (3)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.13:13.1"
msgid "Āraddhavīriyassa uppajjati pīti nirāmisā."
msgstr "When you’re energetic, spiritual rapture arises."

msgctxt "sn54.13:13.2"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, ānanda, bhikkhuno āraddhavīriyassa uppajjati pīti nirāmisā—"
msgstr ""
"At such a time, a mendicant has activated the awakening factor of rapture; "
"they develop it and perfect it."

msgctxt "sn54.13:13.3"
msgid ""
"pītisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, pītisambojjhaṅgaṃ "
"tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, pītisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno "
"bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. (4)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.13:14.1"
msgid "Pītimanassa kāyopi passambhati, cittampi passambhati."
msgstr "When the mind is full of rapture, the body and mind become tranquil."

msgctxt "sn54.13:14.2"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, ānanda, bhikkhuno pītimanassa kāyopi passambhati, cittampi "
"passambhati—"
msgstr ""
"At such a time, a mendicant has activated the awakening factor of "
"tranquility; they develop it and perfect it."

msgctxt "sn54.13:14.3"
msgid ""
"passaddhisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, "
"passaddhisambojjhaṅgaṃ tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, passaddhisambojjhaṅgo "
"tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. (5)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.13:15.1"
msgid "Passaddhakāyassa sukhino cittaṃ samādhiyati."
msgstr ""
"When the body is tranquil and one feels bliss, the mind becomes immersed in "
"samādhi."

msgctxt "sn54.13:15.2"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, ānanda, bhikkhuno passaddhakāyassa sukhino cittaṃ samādhiyati—"
msgstr ""
"At such a time, a mendicant has activated the awakening factor of immersion; "
"they develop it and perfect it."

msgctxt "sn54.13:15.3"
msgid ""
"samādhisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, "
"samādhisambojjhaṅgaṃ tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, samādhisambojjhaṅgo "
"tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. (6)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.13:16.1"
msgid "So tathāsamāhitaṃ cittaṃ sādhukaṃ ajjhupekkhitā hoti."
msgstr "They closely watch over that mind immersed in samādhi."

msgctxt "sn54.13:16.2"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, ānanda, bhikkhu tathāsamāhitaṃ cittaṃ sādhukaṃ ajjhupekkhitā "
"hoti—"
msgstr ""
"At such a time, a mendicant has activated the awakening factor of equanimity;"
" they develop it and perfect it."

msgctxt "sn54.13:16.3"
msgid ""
"upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, "
"upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo "
"tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. (7)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.333"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.13:17.1"
msgid "Yasmiṃ samaye, ānanda, bhikkhu vedanāsu … pe …"
msgstr "Whenever a mendicant meditates by observing an aspect of feelings …"

msgctxt "sn54.13:17.2"
msgid "citte … pe …"
msgstr "mind …"

msgctxt "sn54.13:17.3"
msgid "dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati—"
msgstr "principles,"

msgctxt "sn54.13:17.4"
msgid "upaṭṭhitāssa tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno sati hoti asammuṭṭhā."
msgstr "their mindfulness is established and lucid."

msgctxt "sn54.13:17.5"
msgid "Yasmiṃ samaye, ānanda, bhikkhuno upaṭṭhitā sati hoti asammuṭṭhā—"
msgstr ""
"At such a time, a mendicant has activated the awakening factor of "
"mindfulness; they develop it and perfect it. …"

msgctxt "sn54.13:17.6"
msgid ""
"satisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, satisambojjhaṅgaṃ "
"tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, satisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno "
"bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.13:17.7"
msgid "(Yathā paṭhamaṃ satipaṭṭhānaṃ, evaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ.)"
msgstr ""
"(This should be told in full as for the first kind of mindfulness "
"meditation.)"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc18"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.13:18.1"
msgid "So tathāsamāhitaṃ cittaṃ sādhukaṃ ajjhupekkhitā hoti."
msgstr "They closely watch over that mind immersed in samādhi."

msgctxt "sn54.13:18.2"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, ānanda, bhikkhu tathāsamāhitaṃ cittaṃ sādhukaṃ ajjhupekkhitā "
"hoti—"
msgstr ""
"At such a time, a mendicant has activated the awakening factor of equanimity;"
" they develop it and perfect it."

msgctxt "sn54.13:18.3"
msgid ""
"upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, "
"upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo "
"tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.13:18.4"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ bhāvitā kho, ānanda, cattāro satipaṭṭhānā evaṃ bahulīkatā satta "
"bojjhaṅge paripūrenti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how the four kinds of mindfulness meditation are developed and "
"cultivated so as to fulfill the seven awakening factors."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc19"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.13:19.1"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃ bhāvitā, ānanda, satta bojjhaṅgā kathaṃ bahulīkatā vijjāvimuttiṃ "
"paripūrenti?"
msgstr ""
"And how are the seven awakening factors developed and cultivated so as to "
"fulfill knowledge and freedom?"

msgctxt "sn54.13:19.2"
msgid ""
"Idhānanda, bhikkhu satisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ "
"nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ, dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti … pe … "
"upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ "
"vossaggapariṇāmiṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops the awakening factors of mindfulness, "
"investigation of principles, energy, rapture, tranquility, immersion, and "
"equanimity, which rely on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripen "
"as letting go."

msgctxt "sn54.13:19.3"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ bhāvitā kho, ānanda, satta bojjhaṅgā evaṃ bahulīkatā vijjāvimuttiṃ "
"paripūrentī”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how the seven awakening factors are developed and cultivated so as to "
"fulfill knowledge and freedom.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn54.13:19.4"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
